data.clean_description: This is for anyone who wants to share the love. This is also for situations when a package is reshiped and both show up and you feel like paying for the extra package. Also if you decide you d like to choose another shipping option you can pay the difference here. When chosing the quantity each item is 1 , so if you want to tip 20 then you order 20 for the quantity. THANKS.
data.name: Tip Jar Aka IOU Payments
